'''保羅·馬克·占士·羅賓遜'''（{{lang-en|'''Paul Mark James Robinson'''}}，{{bd|1982年|1月7日|catIdx=Robinson, Paul}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[職業|職業]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)|後衛]]，出身[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]青訓系統，現時效力[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]。

==生平==
羅賓遜出身[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]青訓系統，經歷青訓學院及預備隊而晉身一隊。2002年11月9日於主場2-1擊敗[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]首次上陣，在下半場替補[[达伦·沃德_(1978年出生足球运动员)|-{zh-hans:达伦·沃德; zh-hant:戴倫·禾特;}-]]（Darren Ward）登場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.millwallfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10367~18303,00.html |title=Millwall 2 Preston NE 1 |publisher=[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|''millwallfc.co.uk'']] |date=2002-11-09 |accessdate=2011-09-28 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2003年1月11日主場4-0擊敗[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]初次正選上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2611289.stm |title=Millwall 4-0 Watford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-01-11 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702094931/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2611289.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，三天後在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第三圈重賽對[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|劍橋聯]]，羅賓遜於70分鐘接應[[彼得·史維利|彼得·史維利]]開出的[[角球|角球]]頂入，取得個人首個入球並將比數再度扳平2-2，最終米禾爾反勝3-2晉級第四圈對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/2648499.stm |title=Millwall scrape past Cambridge |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-01-14 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702094844/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/2648499.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於球隊後防傷兵問題嚴重，羅賓遜承時崛起，在各項賽事合共上陣18場。翌季羅賓遜繼續強勢表現，直到2003年11月8日作客1-3負於[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，羅賓遜於追截[[戴倫·亨格比|戴倫·亨格比]]時跌倒，需要用擔架抬離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.millwallfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10367~22678,00.html |title=Norwich City vs Millwall 3 - 1 |publisher=[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|''millwallfc.co.uk'']] |date=2003-01-14 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630141119/https://www.millwallfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10367~22678,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，其後證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[前十字韌帶|前十字韌帶]]重創，因而提早結束球季，僅上陣9場，全部擔任正選。

於傷勢復原後，羅賓遜於2004年12月被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[托奎联足球俱乐部|托基聯]]爭取恢復狀態<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/4122177.stm |title=Millwall loan defender to Torquay |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-12-23 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307174249/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/4122177.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上陣13場後結束借用返回米禾爾<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11735_2327901,00.html |title=Millwall recall Robinson |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-02-24 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310091546/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11735_2327901,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，自此重回正選陣容，2006年3月6日將於季後約滿的羅賓遜與米禾爾續約兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11735_2369131,00.html |title=Robbo pens Lions deal |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-03-06 |accessdate=2011-09-28}}</ref>，但球隊不幸於球季結束後降班[[英甲|英甲]]。羅賓遜其後獲時任領隊[[肯尼·杰基特|肯尼·杰基特]]（Kenny Jackett）委任為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]。2008年夏季有傳羅賓遜轉投[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，但他作出否認並表示非常高興繼續留隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11707_3561422,00.html |title=Senda out, Robinson happy |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2008-05-13 |accessdate=2011-09-28}}</ref>。

近年羅賓遜數度遭受傷患困擾，2009年1月31日主場1-2負於[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]，羅賓遜半場傷出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7858144.stm |title=Millwall 1-2 Scunthorpe |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-01-31 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328110108/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7858144.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後證實足部[[骨折|骨折]]，接受[[手術|手術]]後敷上[[石膏|石膏]]，預計需要缺陣8星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_4896397,00.html |title=Robinson suffers injury blow |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2009-02-05 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308011111/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_4896397,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他趕及在升班附加賽復出，於準決賽對[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]首回合主場擔任沒有上陣的板凳球員<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8034406.stm |title=Millwall 1-0 Leeds |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-09 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2009-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511224252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8034406.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，到次回合作客則在賽事末段上陣穩定軍心，累計2-1淘汰對手<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038226.stm |title=Leeds 1-1 Millwall (agg 1-2) |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-14 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2009-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519011827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038226.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月24日[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]決賽再對[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]，於賽事末段失球反勝為敗，羅賓遜於完場前上陣亦於事無補，最終以2-3落敗錯失升班良機<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |title=Millwall 2-3 Scunthorpe |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-24 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2009-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527093943/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]羅賓遜於2009年9月1日在[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]對[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|班列特]]正式復出，但僅維持了35分鐘便因扭傷[[腳踝|腳踝]]而退下火線，賽後經照射[[X射线|X光]]證實雖然沒有[[骨折|骨折]]，但觸傷[[韌帶|韌帶]]又再需要缺陣5星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5546055,00.html |title=New injury blow for Robinson |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2009-09-09 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202004705/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5546055,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於10月17日作客對[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|史托港]]復出，並為球隊先拔頭籌，加上隊友[[尼尔·哈里斯|尼尔·哈里斯]]演出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，大勝4-0而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8295523.stm |title=Stockport 0-4 Millwall |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913205941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8295523.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年1月28日羅賓遜與米禾爾續約至2013年夏季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5891159,00.html |title=Lions duo extend stays |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-01-28 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202004848/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5891159,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球隊以第3位結束球季，與次席的[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]相差僅1分而錯失直接升班席位，連續兩年參加升班附加賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8632671.stm |title=Millwall 3-2 Swindon |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-08 |accessdate=2017-01-21 |archive-date=2020-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200503031932/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8632671.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。準決賽對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]首回合作客兩無記錄，次回合返回主場羅賓遜頂入1球鎖定2-0勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8682156.stm |title=Millwall 2-0 Huddersfield (agg 2-0) |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-18 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109030829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8682156.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年5月29日再次進軍[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]，決賽面對聯賽閉幕日的腳下敗將[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]，羅賓遜於39分鐘近門建功一箭定江山，1-0小勝奪得來季[[英冠|英冠]]最後一張入場劵<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8701538.stm |title=Millwall 1-0 Swindon |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-29 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802213719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8701538.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，完成他的兒時夢想，以隊長身份帶領球隊射入奠勝球在溫布萊奪冠<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6180987,00.html |title=Robinson revels in dream day |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-05-30 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202004753/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6180987,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[米禾爾2010年至2011年球季|2010/11年球季]]重返[[英冠|英冠]]後的首場賽事，羅賓遜於作客對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]射入為米禾爾鎖定3-0勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8881366.stm |title=Bristol City 0-3 Millwall |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-07 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2010-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100814150808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8881366.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他於12月10日作客1-1賽和[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]又拉傷[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]，於聖誕新年魔鬼賽程期間缺陣3星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6577571,00.html |title=Lions lose skipper for Xmas |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-12-14 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2011-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911124202/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6577571,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他趕及於聖誕新年賽程最後一天復出對[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]。2011年3月12日作客對[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，羅賓遜[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]協助球隊大勝3-0<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9418730.stm |title=Burnley 0-3 Millwall |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-12 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2020-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200118144315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9418730.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一度有望競逐附加賽席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6809973,00.html |title=Jackett eyes play-off spot |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-03-13 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081956/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6809973,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終球隊以中游的第9位成績結束球季，季後羅賓遜隨即接受[[手術|手術]]治理受傷的[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[腱|肌腱]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6939219,00.html |title=Lions quartet go under the knife |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-05-18 |accessdate=2011-09-28}}</ref>。

2011年8月[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]求購羅賓遜<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_7117744,00.html |title=Royals eye Robinson move |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-08-22 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041417/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_7117744,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但因出價過低而遭拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_7118560,00.html |title=Royals fail with Robinson bid |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-08-22 |accessdate=2011-09-28}}</ref>。

